{"tid":2081204,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"史上第一次無七一遊行？","createTime":"2020-06-27T05:00:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T08:29:27.000Z","uid":7542,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"120a85b64f206b761fd25d6d1e8b7ea5d9408ad3","tid":2081204,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T05:00:04.000Z","msg":"「港版國安法」立法在即，有民主派人士計劃分別於明日(6月28日)及7月1日舉辦集會、遊行表達不滿，惟昨日(26日)同遭警方發出反對通知書。民主派人士隨即提出上訴申請。公眾集會及遊行上訴委員會今早(27日)召開聆訊，最終以遊行有違公眾安全、秩序及安全為由，決定維持反對舉辦上述兩場遊行、集會。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人，你會點做？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/i7ZF_dgqG3s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fi7ZF_dgqG3s&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFnKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=c3699198\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/i7ZF_dgqG3s</a>"},{"pid":"d4bef0bd67f30dd6d8e12e260271a0a8f6e088dd","tid":2081204,"uid":223643,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T05:00:25.000Z","msg":"七一見"},{"pid":"96e96bfcb6dd7780fda82f4851f9d583bec1bc70","tid":2081204,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T05:00:35.000Z","msg":"Source: <a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200627/bkn-20200627124406888-0627_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200627%2Fbkn-20200627124406888-0627_00822_001.html&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFnKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=85fb8c5f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200627/bkn-20200627124406888-0627_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"28be907647e5106edb80970c6b53b057a71a126c","tid":2081204,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4bef0bd67f30dd6d8e12e260271a0a8f6e088dd","tid":2081204,"uid":223643,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T05:00:25.000Z","msg":"七一見"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T05:01:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" 